The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Indira honour
                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                      Indira honour
                            
	Dhaka, Aug. 21 (PTI): Bangladesh will honour Indira Gandhi for her immense support in its struggle for liberation on the countrys 40th independence day next year. She will be honoured as part of a plan to acknowledge the role of foreign leaders in the 1971 war.                                                                                                                                                           
